{"pageProps":{"currentData":{"ID":853333,"author":"1","author_nickname":"wpuser","author_display_name":"Chuckie Chang","author_url":"https://matrixflip.com/api","author_username":"wpuser","author_avatar":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=96&d=mm&r=g","categories":[87],"categories_output":[{"ID":87,"slug":"%e5%bc%80%e5%8f%91%e8%b6%a3%e5%91%b3","name":"开发趣味","term_taxonomy_id":87,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":0,"count":17}],"tags":[101,103,100,104,105,96,102],"tags_output":[{"ID":101,"slug":"frontend","name":"frontend","term_taxonomy_id":101,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":2},{"ID":103,"slug":"mac","name":"mac","term_taxonomy_id":103,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1},{"ID":100,"slug":"react","name":"react","term_taxonomy_id":100,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":3},{"ID":104,"slug":"windows","name":"windows","term_taxonomy_id":104,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1},{"ID":105,"slug":"%e4%b9%a6%e7%ad%be%e7%ae%a1%e7%90%86","name":"书签管理","term_taxonomy_id":105,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1},{"ID":96,"slug":"%e5%89%8d%e7%ab%af%e5%bc%80%e5%8f%91","name":"前端开发","term_taxonomy_id":96,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":10},{"ID":102,"slug":"%e6%a1%8c%e9%9d%a2%e5%ba%94%e7%94%a8","name":"桌面应用","term_taxonomy_id":102,"term_group":0,"taxonomy":"post_tag","description":"","parent":0,"count":1}],"thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_f625296ac99ba6ff53de68ca-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfacbaffdecaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_f625296ac99ba6ff53de68ca-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfacbaffdecaxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_f625296ac99ba6ff53de68ca-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfacbaffdecaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_full":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_f625296ac99ba6ff53de68ca-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomfacbaffdecaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"date_day":"23","date_month":"01","date_month_e":"January","date_year":"2022","date_weekday":"Sunday","title":"创建一个有趣的书签(收藏夹)管理器「跨平台桌面应用F-Curator」","excerpt":"为了应对自己的一些网站管理需求，自己开发了一个自用桌面应用程序 F-Curator，方便离线管理收藏的网页","content":"<p><span>互联网上有很多书签管理工具或网站平台，但要选择一个合适的并不容易。 在过去几年的工作和学习中，我一直有这个硬性需求。 如何离线管理自己的网址列表成为了一个必不可少的提高工作和学习效率的事情。使用联网的平台，一旦网站关闭或者网络不好，就没了数据，不方便管理。虽然类似于谷歌浏览器自带的书签已经很好用，甚至有远程同步功能，但为了更好的将数据保存到本机，永远不会丢失，方便快捷的管理。自己开发了一个自用桌面应用程序 </span><a href=\"https://xizon.github.io/F-Curator-Official-Website/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">F-Curator</a><span>，方便离线管理收藏的网页。</span></p>\n<p>我具体的说一说设计和开发思路，首先参考一下Google Chrome自带的书签管理功能，这是我自己电脑上的截图：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/c736ef9827b115c63059ca5a-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadscefbccaajpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> </p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/5495abaaeee7b83c92602bd4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsabaaeeebcbdjpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<h3>想法</h3>\n<p>因为自己本身存在这个硬性需求，于是设计了一个可以在没有互联网的情况下进行管理的书签应用程序（网页 URL 的管理/收集），这解决了我的问题。 正式版已经发布，支持macOS和Windows系统。下图是F-Curator基本的工作流程：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/static-remote/files/745c4bb145c03cadd9fac94e-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadscbbccaddfacejpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=465841859&amp;bvid=BV1k5411f7nP&amp;cid=488570276&amp;page=1\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\"> </iframe></p>\n<p></p>\n<h4></h4>\n<h3>实现技术：</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">应用主要基于React、Electron、Node，业余开发爱好者，有web基础的大神就可以忽略：）给个支持给个建议。</span></p>\n<h4>接下来，对整个应用做一个简单的介绍</h4>\n<p>F-Curator 是一个跨平台应用程序，支持Mac和Windows系统，用来管理您自己的网络收藏夹，永久保存数据，解决用户的URL收藏需求。</p>\n<h3>主要功能：</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>离线支持和快速的响应速度</li>\n<li>轻松实现数据持久化</li>\n<li>获取远程资源到本地数据库</li>\n<li>类别管理和列表块管理</li>\n<li>简单的拖放排序</li>\n<li>导出独立的HTML文件，可以脱离APP在任意操作系统中使用收藏夹</li>\n<li>支持导入数据库包</li>\n<li>支持快速搜索URL和站点名称</li>\n<li>URL有效性和重复性的判断</li>\n<li>自动提取远程资源，例如图标</li>\n</ol>\n<p>未来，我会继续完善它的功能，以更好地提高我的工作效率。 并尝试更多有趣的事情。 我希望这个开源应用可以给你带来一些用处。</p>\n</p>\n<h3>最后的话语</h3>\n<p>感谢您花几分钟阅读，有需要的可以直接下载使用：）</p>\n<p>官方网站：<a href=\"https://xizon.github.io/F-Curator-Official-Website/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://xizon.github.io/F-Curator-Official-Website/</a></p>\n<p>Electron官方入口：<a href=\"https://www.electronjs.org/apps/f-curator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.electronjs.org/apps/f-curator</a></p>\n","slug":"95f548db46d3d3bc922c57f4","prev":[{"ID":843333,"title":"使用React从零完整构建一个不错的网站「PoemKit的诞生」","excerpt":"沉醉于Web开发，我认为是一件富有诗意和美好的事情。我们可以用各种优秀的前端技术、UI组件和无限的可能性来点缀我们的想法。天马行空，总有我想做，我能做，我不能做的。 在这些过程中，很容易忘记我们为什么坚持这样做，以及一个不错的漂亮的的网站究竟是什么？","slug":"c9b2efad300f04dec769c6b8","post_date":"2021-11-12 17:07:09","post_date_gmt":"2021-11-12 17:07:09","thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_146063ac038bbbd804602bea-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomacbbbdbeaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_146063ac038bbbd804602bea-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomacbbbdbeaxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_146063ac038bbbd804602bea-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomacbbbdbeaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"next":[{"ID":863333,"title":"个人Scrum敏捷开发转型中的技术实践","excerpt":"Scrum无处不在，说起Scrum敏捷开发框架，也许大家并不陌生，表面理解它其实并不复杂，但是真正用得好的公司并不多，我自己曾经的工作环境也依然没有体验过敏捷开发非常成熟的实践过程，但是我依然推荐这种开发方式，不论是对于企业发展还是生活中的任意角落。不过我今天并不是谈论企业中的敏捷开发，自己近半年的空窗期间，在努力尝试个人的Scrum转型。","slug":"personal-scrum-agile-development-technology-practice","post_date":"2022-04-03 22:16:00","post_date_gmt":"2022-04-03 22:16:00","thumbnail":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_d9e2ce8091f89999ebe5a624-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomdecefebeaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false],"thumbnail_mini":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_d9e2ce8091f89999ebe5a624-770x340-4-150x150-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomdecefebeaxxjpg.jpg",150,150,true],"thumbnail_retina":["/static-remote/files/c945-com_d9e2ce8091f89999ebe5a624-770x340-4-matrixflipcomapiwpcontentuploadsccomdecefebeaxjpg.jpg",770,340,false]}],"post_date":"2022-01-23 00:07:14","post_date_gmt":"2022-01-23 00:07:14","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","post_password":"","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2022-01-23 00:07:14","post_modified_gmt":"2022-01-23 00:07:14","post_content_filtered":"","post_parent":0,"guid":"https://matrixflip.com/api/?post_type=post&amp;p=853333","menu_order":0,"post_type":"post","post_mime_type":"","comment_count":"0","filter":"raw"},"postID":"95f548db46d3d3bc922c57f4"},"__N_SSG":true}